898
00:52:32.052 --> 00:52:35.992
So bladder cancer is the number ninth most common cancer type around the world,

899
00:52:36.292 --> 00:52:39.612
and the majority of bladder cancer is urothelial carcinoma, which

900
00:52:39.832 --> 00:52:43.812
