903
00:52:52.412 --> 00:52:55.731
invasive and muscle invasive bladder cancer, which is

904
00:52:56.072 --> 00:52:59.852
apparently a more aggressive disease with worse prognosis and

905
00:53:00.272 --> 00:53:02.412
