911
00:53:22.012 --> 00:53:25.592
pembrolizumab has become a new standard of care for

912
00:53:25.812 --> 00:53:29.392
bladder patient with an advanced disease.

913
00:53:29.422 --> 00:53:33.232
And lineage plasticity is one of the cancer hallmarks describing the

914
00:53:33.272 --> 00:53:36.292
cell's ability to change between different cell states.

915
00:53:36.752 --> 00:53:40.672
And in bladder cancer, this can further manifest as the morphologic

916
00:53:40.752 --> 00:53:44.532
heterogeneity that the pathologists usually use the

917
00:53:44.612 --> 00:53:47.132
