00:55:12.752 --> 00:55:14.732
histologic variants.

941
00:55:14.812 --> 00:55:18.304
AndEspecially in the expression of lineage

942
00:55:18.364 --> 00:55:22.084
markers and ADC targets. So overall, we think

943
00:55:22.164 --> 00:55:25.944
