1189
01:09:06.717 --> 01:09:10.416
currently known translation initiation factors across

1190
01:09:10.476 --> 01:09:14.416
different AML cell lines, and found that eIF4A1

1191
01:09:14.456 --> 01:09:18.036
is the most highly expressed translation initiation factor.

1192
01:09:19.516 --> 01:09:22.496
